text: Matar Dieye (born 10 January 1998) is a Senegalese football player. He plays in Croatia for HNK Gorica. ==Club career== He started his career in Italian fourth-tier Serie D with Sacilese. He made his Serie B debut for Vicenza on 23 April 2016 in a game against Spezia, as an 86th-minute substitute for Filip Raičević. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Senegalese footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:A.S.D.
